@startuml
title Document Processing Pipeline

start
:Register upload or export request;
:Create Document / Job record;
:Store raw artifact metadata;
:Parse with format adapter;
if (Validation passed?) then (yes)
  :Build preview and reconciliation result;
  if (Operator confirms commit?) then (yes)
    :Execute business command;
    :Write audit trail and artifact links;
    :Mark job completed;
  else (no)
    :Mark job canceled;
  endif
else (no)
  :Persist validation errors;
  :Mark job failed;
endif
stop
@enduml
